&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 PROJECT      molecular_states
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
&END

&TOPOL
 connectivity   generate
 coord_file     sample_pdb/water_32.pdb
 coordinate     pdb
&END

&SETUP
  cell
    parameter 9.865  0.000   0.000 &
              0.000  9.865   0.000 &
              0.000  0.000   9.865
  end cell
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   Pade
&END

&QS
 CUTOFF       200
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        ATOMIC
 MIXING       0.4
 EPS_SCF      1.0E-5
&END

&PRINT LOW
 LOCALIZATION
 MOLECULAR_STATES
&END
 DISTRIBUTION

&KIND H
 BASIS_SET    DZV-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH
&END

&KIND O
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          9.865 9.865 9.865
&END
